| Cryptocurrency exchange calculator |

This script is a very simple script to run.  No extra pluggins are required to run this script.  In short, you will download the cryptocurrency.py, 
then just simply run the script.  From there, you will be asked how much USD you want to convert to a specific crypto.  So for example, if you wanted to
convert USD to Bitcoin, you will enter "1" in the input.  After that, you will input how much you want to convert.  After hitting enter again, it will
display the conversion price of your entered amount of USD to Bitcoin!
